    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain remains tight with a factory limited-slip differential providing excellent power delivery. Suspension is sorted with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the chassis's legendary balance. While the exterior shows honest road patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains a high-revving masterpiece with a linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. A technically sound specimen for the discerning purist.",
