      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is in excellent mechanical health. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though it shows minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small curb scuff on the rear passenger alloy wheel\u2014typical for its mileage but otherwise very clean. The interior is smoke-free, featuring Agate Grey leather seats that remain firm and supportive with no rips or thinning. Key features include the Premium Package Plus, panoramic sunroof, and a Bose surround-sound system. All service is up to date, including a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection performed last month. The brakes are responsive, and the tires show plenty of life. This Macan delivers a sharp, responsive driving experience and comes with a full set of service records and two original key fobs.",
